doctype html
html
  head
    extends templates/layout
    block title
        link(rel='stylesheet', href='Terraria/stylesheets/index.css')
        script(type='text/javascript', src='https://cdn.socket.io/socket.io-1.3.5.js')    
        script(src='http://code.jquery.com/jquery-latest.min.js')
        script(type='text/javascript', src='javascripts/chat.js') 
        meta(name="description", content="Cubiversum Terraria is a server for Terraria. We have friendly staff, skilled builders, and tons of incredible creations. The only thing missing is you!")
        meta(property="og:site_name", content="Cubiversum Terraria")
        meta(property="og:image", content="http://cubiversum.com/general/images/logo.png")
        meta(property="og:type", content="website")
        meta(property="og:url" content="http://cubiversum.com")
        meta(property="og:title", content="Cubiversum Terraria")
        title Cubiversum Terraria
  body
    block append header
    block prepend footer
        .content
            .title Hello and welcome to Cubiversum!
            //.msgbox
                .header
                   p(id='title') Cubiversum Chatbox
                #messages
                    .msg
                        p(id='user') Ancientgods:
                        p(id='body') This chatbox is under construction, you are currently talking to yourself!
                .input
                    input(id='msgbox', type='text', placeholder='Type your message here', onkeydown='if(event.keyCode == 13) AddMsg();')

            .msg
                #msgheader
                    p(class='msgtitle') Please help us keep the server alive.
                    p(class='msgdate') 2015-06-10
                #body
                    p Hey Terrarians! If you enjoy playing on Cubiversum, why not give us a donation? 
                    p Your contributions will help us cover costs associated with running the server so we can improve the experience for everybody!
                    p Help us keep the lights on; your support is much appreciated!
                    br
                    form(action='https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr', method='post', target='_top')
                        input(type='hidden', name='cmd', value='_s-xclick')
                        input(type='hidden', name='hosted_button_id', value='TB9QAKQFZ9DTS')
                        input(type='image', src='https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donate_LG.gif', border='0', name='submit', alt='PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!')
                        img(alt='', border='0', src='https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif', width='1', height='1')
            .msg
                #msgheader
                    p(class='msgtitle') Vote vote vote!
                    p(class='msgdate') 2015-06-09
                #body
                    p Hello guys, please vote for our server as it helps us making this server more popular. Below you will find a link to vote.
                    p After you've voted (be sure to fill in your name in the name field) you can claim a reward by waiting 1-4 minutes.
                    br
                    script(src="http://terraria-servers.com/embed.js?id=1065&type=votes&size=normal")
                    br
                    p Thank you and have a nice day!
            .msg
                #msgheader
                    p(class='msgtitle') To-do List
                    p(class='msgdate') 2015-06-09
                #body
                    #todo
                        h3 Already finished (With great help of magnusi):
                        ul
                            li Added a functional login page that uses ingame accounts.
                            li Created an admin page that is not viewable by non-superadmins.
                            li Created an awesome menu bar :3 (barman approves)
                            li Made a footer that sticks to the bottom of the page.
                        br
                        h3 Todo List:
                        ul
                            li Create more content for admin page.
                            li Add a neat-looking chatbox that interacts with the server's chat
                            li Add a gallery (suggestion by Jewsus)
                            li Add a command to automaticly create snapshots ingame and send them to the gallery.
                            li Add visitor tracker to stats page.
            .msg
                #msgheader
                    p(class='msgtitle') Welcome to our server!
                    p(class='msgdate') 2015-05-27
                #body
                    p Welcome to our brand new server, Cubiversum!
                    br
                    p This server is created by:
                    ul
                        br
                        li Ancientgods
                        li RJ Somebody
                        li Magnusi




